item.title: CVE-2017-9510|2024-10-16T14:03:34.200Z -- atlassian -- atlassian%20fisheye
item.description: The repository changelog resource in Atlassian Fisheye before version 4.4.1 allows remote attackers to inject arbitrary HTML or JavaScript via a cross site scripting (XSS) vulnerability through the start date and end date parameters.
